{
  "texts": [
    "We provide a set of insights based on existing work in Table 1.",
    "The present pattern of published papers on the use of LLMs for cyber defense indicates that most studies are focused on the detection and protection roles of LLMs aligning with the NIST framework.",
    "However, a research gap, as shown in Figure 1, becomes evident in post-attack scenarios.",
    "Given the critical roles recovery and attack response play in the cybersecurity lifecycle, it is essential that further studies be centered around the development of innovative LLM-related solutions to maximize their potential in productive post-attack scenarios.",
    "Applications of LLMs in cybersecurity extend beyond techniques for defense."
  ]
}